data.description: Unique property just outside Burlington City Limits on Hwy 20.  This property has a very nice 2007 1782 manufactured home.  The home has a large kitchen with beautiful cabinets, lot of storage, large living room with vaulted ceiling, large bedrooms with  walk in closets.   Property also has detached dbl car garage, a wood working shop, and a 1500+ building that was previously used for an antique business and a couple other buildings as well.   This property has so much potential!  Must see to appreciate all it has to offer!
